text: John Scott Duarte (born September 9, 1966) is an American politician, businessman, and farmer. A member of the Republican Party, he was the U.S. representative for California's 13th congressional district from 2023 to 2025. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Modesto, California
